s</a>"},{"pid":"bbdebeb3cf0b2da996fe8a939e355e6d613f69cf","tid":1575983,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"由6月12號到今日<br />\n所有被所謂速龍防暴虐待毆打拘捕嘅人<br />\n佢地係違法執行職務 普通市民亦無法確認佢係咪正式錄用嘅警察 著套衫就係？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見到一班冇編號冇委任證嘅懷疑冒警武裝恐怖分子持槍襲擊香港市民<br />\n即使衝擊佢又何罪之有？</span></span><br />\n而且一直以嚟我地先係被衝擊虐打殘害施襲嘅一方"},{"pid":"0768d6ea73c953ab5e415ef9bb1a6cd5cc640c0d","tid":1575983,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f1521029b25ee33861d418992a71ff3a870befb","tid":1575983,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:09:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28715a8e313b7dbfb1e7f34d119bf9964a40f4d8","tid":1575983,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4af1b776f56412aa6e49d53a1cf3b6d5991b5d1b","tid":1575983,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:10:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c739064cb5e2f8a726c275943e511232305646b","tid":1575983,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73d63c7b1b8e27f2f18de97d9a12fb8dab143928","tid":1575983,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:11:27.000Z","msg":"其實連登唔缺頭腦，係缺人手，所以應該更加推行人人文宣，得閒黐幾張"},{"pid":"7cf061ed66e7a683bae7e5f6b1d53505538b3b6f","tid":1575983,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"1/50"},{"pid":"89750eeca96191c0ccfb71dbf8be87a88eedea6d","tid":1575983,"uid":289160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc629a3fd6daff58ec826cf7a9019ee8b752b3a0","tid":1575983,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:13:35.000Z","msg":"2/50"},{"pid":"8bb66c760f01ea79